7663c85d8158603aaba572978df6a1f4e7a76","tid":1049333,"uid":202340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:07:11.000Z","msg":"手信應該係自己揀畀人<br />\n人哋叫你幫手買嗰啲就唔係手信啦"},{"pid":"0118842d754324092548cabe49fa5858c20f5cd3","tid":1049333,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"會唔會你一開始同佢講到明唔順路所以唔買好d<br />\n宜家佢以為你會買 點知你買個環保袋返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c200b0ddeea0bbefb7cb37b217fc464f262492","tid":1049333,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"除咗屋企人之外<br />\n我叫人買or人哋幫我買，我都講明:你/我咁啱經過見到又記得又得閒又有心情先幫你/我買"},{"pid":"bb4a563282c1e3fc606920218ed29979791f878a","tid":1049333,"uid":52271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T11:28:13.000Z","msg":"老母叫到就做啦<br />\n唔熟嘅同事朋友就話啫"},{"pid":"5d8d000ba228b5e12492b09051b8e516cebad419","tid":1049333,"uid":24296,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:52:10.000Z","msg":"屋企人就買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n養到你咁大叫你幫小小忙都唔得"},{"pid":"fec6ab10384b26519496dc9a79063d436b7a595f","tid":1049333,"uid":907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:00:51.000Z","msg":"屌你幾百萬養大你<br />\n叫你去買個袋都係到阿支阿左<br />\n送個袋比老母都得掛"},{"pid":"19d2b2402946a5f69a5a692358edf84140cd7007","tid":1049333,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"所以都係叫朋友買明信片 算 幾靚"},{"pid":"f94a16b7f08323ac9c7733a9ff37c17c646b07f1","tid":1049333,"uid":1703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"呢d老母就係d死仆街港女進化而成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世界必然要圍住佢轉咁<br />\n唔好同我講咩養大你買少少野都唔得<br />\n你生得我出就係有責任要養大我<br />\n蝕唔起就唔好生 一係送去保良局<br />\n唔死都冇用呀？係呀 有個呢d老母真係慘過去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20ad939c9eef2ae0b8642d1afc6cc027a32e5fc","tid":1049333,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:50:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔識拒絕嘅人仲黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca3092653ef26355bb347a1adf0dfa0d0dd515a","tid":1049333,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:52:35.000Z","msg":"咪唔買 你話搵唔到/唔順路/唔記得佢咬你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004e88b86f5fec922ddd4beda50d44a300ac4848","tid":1049333,"uid":1703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"不過樓主你買唔到/唔想買咪求撚其話冇貨/間野執左買唔到之類囉 手袋都要人幫佢買佢都唔會識得上網睇上網訂架啦<br />\n一早講定俾佢知返到黎係唔會有手袋俾到佢<br />\n咁佢就唔會咁失望 <br />\n再講多次<br />\n人地唔買俾佢就發癲係好撚幼稚好似三歲細路扭計咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手袋救佢唔到 要去睇精神科醫生先岩"},{"pid":"e53fc974f100949d1d235b927410673ecef9a01c","tid":1049333,"uid":201482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:56:17.000Z","msg":"樓主，你老母覺得個手袋重要過你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb44b93e53c8b93e5cb7189252fec2756df802fe","tid":1049333,"uid":224452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T08:00:00.000Z","msg":"我從來唔會有「去旅行幫人買野」嘅概念<br />\n除非我主動想送野俾佢，我就會順路隨便買（當然會按返我對佢嘅喜好認知去買）"},{"pid":"b1cdc2287e8da13ed1ab7630ddfc20428764ca28","tid":1049333,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T08:01:35.000Z","msg":"老母咋嘛 一句買唔到幾咁閒<br />\n駛乜打咁大段野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc3ecc09796da190e10333df79a1372cba262d2","tid":1049333,"uid":26302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T08:58:16.000Z","msg":"港女老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來都覺得自己想要既野係要自己去買"}]}